":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:20:59.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"07c03efe18e849700ad83f994487d8260250eb3d","tid":1625974,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc484d93e800851388d3f5e1b38c61676c5cc14","tid":1625974,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e64757e2420b203508e4300c506cceb9e7dc71d3","tid":1625974,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDPai6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDPai6a.png&h=d0972ecd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:17:27.000Z","msg":"琴日都己經係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:40:54.000Z","msg":"琴日冇up 圖 所以唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}